  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "YmReIIE28WWxyKeAlzYr8Vzl5PPJ4iHYyPJbjah80kc=",
    "originContent": "The pure-C DSP layer (`dsp/`) has a small unit test suite exercising ADSR envelope boundaries, the note stack, unison detune math, pitch-bend propagation, and delay-line feedback stability. Tests are opt-in so they don't affect normal plugin builds:",
    "translatedContent": "纯 C 语言的 DSP 层（`dsp/`）有一个小型单元测试套件，测试 ADSR 包络边界、音符堆栈、合奏微调数学、弯音传播和延迟线反馈稳定性。测试是可选的，因此不会影响正常插件构建："
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "NEP53d++GBwJqrj1uGCH4G6VQpxuy2zhx3z9y0n41S8=",
    "originContent": "cd cpp",
    "translatedContent": "cd cpp"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "Dgofk15Bo/vQzE6IdMrZexW2jS4As2INIoVeXydPBeg=",
    "originContent": "cmake -B build-tests -DMONKSYNTH_BUILD_TESTS=ON",
    "translatedContent": "cmake -B build-tests -DMONKSYNTH_BUILD_TESTS=ON"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "NYgrF3GdALCtYkA/+vcUAO6Z1dU247jl1AX5dWB4lWA=",
    "originContent": "cmake --build build-tests --config Release",
    "translatedContent": "cmake --build build-tests --config Release"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "nBxObvzVCg3hA9KSbZMGHn5l6m+qbHGQbj23Y80LNSA=",
    "originContent": "ctest --test-dir build-tests --output-on-failure",
    "translatedContent": "ctest --test-dir build-tests --output-on-failure"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "wIgJWKFbr6fS8QMuP7zmUtDWKOm1HeZ0hVlR5kbCOXo=",
    "originContent": "CI runs the test suite on the Linux job before packaging each release, so any DSP regression blocks the build.",
    "translatedContent": "CI 在 Linux 任务上运行测试套件，然后才打包每个版本，因此任何 DSP 回归都会阻止构建。"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
