  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "DdmNh2jVyoC3agYanom+m0GxUBJqncSEv0ra3ndfQK0=",
    "originContent": "**Looking for fresh default themes to ship with the plugin.** If you design a theme you're proud of, open a PR — I'd love to include contributed themes in the next release. The right-click menu has an \"Open Themes Folder\" item that reveals where themes live on disk.",
    "translatedContent": "**正在寻找新的默认主题以随插件一起发布。** 如果您设计了令您自豪的主题，请提交 PR — 我很乐意在下次发布中包含贡献的主题。右键菜单中有“打开主题文件夹”项，可显示主题在磁盘上的位置。"
  },
  {
